{
  "stem": "14060.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There were two nations who really, actively assisted the Jews as such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And these were the Danes, where the king himself, as it's known, said, I put on a red-- a yellow star if my Jewish people have to, and helped them to escape to Sweden, and the Serbs.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Serbs being great Catholics-- and I don't hold up any great torches, that the Greek Orthodox, who were basically the Russian religion, were so tremendously nice over all the centuries to Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But as it happens, maybe because the Serbs were suffering under the, the, the, the persecution of the Ustase of the Croats-- who are the worst Nazis.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I mean, there they hardly had to deport people because they killed them on the spot like in Lithuania and Latvia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "These were the couple of places where they didn't have to bother to deport them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They killed them on the spot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I don't think it is not worth remembering that today's president of Croatia has written a book in which he is basically dismissing the whole Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And maybe today for political reasons he is backtracking on it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But the Croatians have got a terrible history.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I'm very sorry if individual people got killed or maimed there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "But they have got a great responsibility what they did during the Second World War, what happened now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And this is far from understood by the Western nations, who don't know the ethnic differences and the background from where all this trouble has come from.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The Balkans have always been the cause of world wars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "The first world war started there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "So that I leave out because this is not really a Jewish matter.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
